{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-aktuell-js","path":"/aktuell/","result":{"data":{"allJsonJson":{"edges":[{"node":{"published":"2019-11-16","title":"Pt11 - Ornithoplanes","tags":["Roadkill App","Rewild Karpaten","Vegetal city","The Hunter","Sitspot"],"newsletter":"<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\"\n       style=\"width:100%;\">\n    <tbody>\n    <tr>\n        <td style=\"border:0px solid #ffffff;direction:ltr;font-size:0px;padding:20px 0px 20px 0px;padding-bottom:20px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:20px;text-align:center;\">\n            <!--[if mso | IE]>\n            <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n                <tr>\n                    <td style=\"vertical-align:top;width:600px;\"><![endif]-->\n            <div class=\"mj-column-per-100 mj-outlook-group-fix\"\n                 style=\"font-size:0px;text-align:left;direction:ltr;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:100%;\">\n                <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\"\n                       style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"100%\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <td align=\"left\"\n                            style=\"font-size:0px;padding:10px 25px;padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:20px;word-break:break-word;\">\n                            <div style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22px;text-align:left;color:#5e6977;\">\n                                <h2 style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                                    Hi,<br>zu Teil 11 von\n                                    Ivo's<span> </span><span>Ecotainment</span><span> </span><span>Newsletter</span>!\n                                </h2></div>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td align=\"left\"\n                            style=\"font-size:0px;padding:10px 25px;padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:0px;word-break:break-word;\">\n                            <div style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22px;text-align:left;color:#5e6977;\">\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">Another best of the\n                                    econet!</p>\n                                <h3 style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                                    1. Roadkill App</h3>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">Plattgefahrene Tiere entlang\n                                    der Straßen sind leider überall.<br>Die App “<a target=\"_blank\"\n                                                                                    href=\"https://roadkill.at\"\n                                                                                    style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">Roadkill</a>”\n                                    aus Österreich sammelt die Daten um die Hotspots zu entschärfen.\n                                    Mensch fühlt sich gleich viel besser...</p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\"><a target=\"_blank\"\n                                                                               href=\"https://roadkill.at\"\n                                                                               style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">https://roadkill.at</a>\n                                </p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\"><i\n                                        style=\"font-style:italic\">#citizen science #digital relief\n                                    #unobstrusive roads #mitmachen #geodata #fallwild</i><br></p>\n                                <h3 style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                                    2. Rewild Karpaten</h3>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">An der Donau werden\n                                    Wasserbüffel ausgewildert, die ein junger Forstwissenschaftler aus\n                                    Kiel in der Ukraine züchtet.<br>Großwild soll dort wieder die\n                                    Landschaft formen.<br><a target=\"_blank\"\n                                                             href=\"https://news.mongabay.com/2019/10/why-is-europe-rewilding-with-water-buffalo/\"\n                                                             style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">https://news.mongabay.com/2019/10/why-is-europe-rewilding-with-water-buffalo</a>\n                                </p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">Auch interessant: Der Typ\n                                    betreibt in der Ukraine eine Art Arche für alte Haustierrassen,\n                                    autarke osteuropäische Lebensweisen und Aussteiger.</p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\"><a target=\"_blank\"\n                                                                               href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIb5EUU1ti4\"\n                                                                               style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">Michels\n                                    call for action facing endangered cultures in Ukraine</a>, 5:16m,\n                                    Youtube</p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\"><i\n                                        style=\"font-style:italic\">#wilder osten #rewild #downshifting\n                                    #werde Aussteiger und Hirte #Michel Jacobi</i><br></p>\n                                <h3 style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                                    3. Utopist</h3>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">Luc Schuiten -“L'architecte\n                                    visionnaire bruxellois”- ist Architekt, Comic-Zeichner und Utopist\n                                    aus Brüssel.<br>Toller TED Talk über Städte als Wälder:<br><a\n                                            target=\"_blank\"\n                                            href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_n5EPkM_q8\"\n                                            style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">TEDxNantes\n                                        - Luc Schuiten</a>, 17:52m, Youtube</p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">TL;DW<br>Auf citi.io und auf\n                                    seiner Webseite gibt es eine Zusammenfassung seines Œuvres:</p>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <li><a target=\"_blank\"\n                                           href=\"https://citi.io/2015/07/24/how-future-cities-may-look-more-like-natural-forest-and-why-it-matters/\"\n                                           style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">https://citi.io/2015/07/24/how-future-cities-may-look-more-like-natural-forest-and-why-it-matters/</a>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.vegetalcity.net/\"\n                                           style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">https://www.vegetalcity.net</a>\n                                    </li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\"><i\n                                        style=\"font-style:italic\">#ornithoplanes #baumhaus #BD\n                                    Franco-Belge</i><br></p>\n                                <h3 style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                                    4. Rastafari bun dem Halali</h3>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">Anti Jagd Reggae:<br><a\n                                        target=\"_blank\"\n                                        href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gXx5Phl0gW8\"\n                                        style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">The Hunter -\n                                    Clinton Fearon</a>, 4:50m , Youtube<br><a target=\"_blank\"\n                                                                              href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3oZpr5mf6TnYG7Tuf45f3g\"\n                                                                              style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">https://open.spotify.com/track/3oZpr5mf6TnYG7Tuf45f3g</a>\n                                </p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\"><i\n                                        style=\"font-style:italic\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><i\n                                        style=\"font-style:normal\">Passende Petition:</i></span> <a\n                                        target=\"_blank\"\n                                        href=\"https://mitmachen.nabu.de/turteltauben-retten\"\n                                        style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">Jagdverbot\n                                    für den Vogel des Jahres: die Turteltaube</a><br><br>Beim <a\n                                        target=\"_blank\"\n                                        href=\"https://www.nabu.de/news/2019/11/27181.html\"\n                                        style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">Brachvogel\n                                    in Frankreich</a> hat eine Petition geholfen!</i></p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">#turteltaube #ringeltaube\n                                    #türkentaube #hohltaube #felsentaube #luftratte #irie<br></p>\n                                <h3 style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                                    5. Trend-Sport Sitzen</h3>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">Jeder braucht einen <span\n                                        style=\"font-weight:700\"><b\n                                        style=\"font-weight:700\">Sitspot</b></span>!<br>Ein Ort an den\n                                    man regelmäßig geht, einfach eine Weile sitzt und “ganzheitlich”\n                                    beobachtet. Über die Zeit kommt die Erkenntnis von ganz allein.</p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\"><i\n                                        style=\"font-style:italic\">“A sit spot (or secret spot) is simply\n                                    a favorite place in nature that you visit regularly to cultivate\n                                    awareness as you expand your senses and study patterns of local\n                                    plants, birds, trees, animals, etc.”</i><br><br>Good long read: <a\n                                        target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://nature-mentor.com/sit-spot/\"\n                                        style=\"color: #1c80ff; text-decoration: underline;\">https://nature-mentor.com/sit-spot/</a>\n                                </p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">#achtsam abgammeln #birders\n                                    bench #waldbaden #betonbaden #spoten</p></div>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td align=\"left\"\n                            style=\"font-size:0px;padding:10px 25px;padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:0px;word-break:break-word;\">\n                            <div style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22px;text-align:left;color:#5e6977;\">\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">That's all folks !</p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">Tracking ist aus!<br>Feedback,\n                                    Forwards, Fuckyous an hello@ivo-bathke.name</p>\n                                <p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 10px 0;\">You're welcome!</p></div>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </table>\n            </div>\n            <!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]--></td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n</div><!--[if mso | IE]></td></tr></table><![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><!--[if mso | IE]>\n"}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":true}}}